        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Justice for Exonerees Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases the maximum amount of damages that an individual who was unjustly convicted and incarcerated may be awarded and requires that this amount be adjusted annually for inflation.</p>]]>
        </text>
